headline: JPMorgan Raises Ralph Lauren (RL) Price Target, Keeps Overweight Rating
summary: On Thursday, May 22, JPMorgan analyst Matthew Boss kept an “Overweight” rating and raised the price target for Ralph Lauren Corporation (NYSE:RL) to $355 from $342.
